{"tid":550988,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港聞 【新東補選】趙佩玉稱天父指她一定贏　3.11有神蹟","createTime":"2018-02-05T09:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T10:04:45.000Z","uid":29540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df4dd2a374198c461357f09888c6f5f1e530df06","tid":550988,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:07:38.000Z","msg":"新界東參選人出席商台論壇，參選人趙佩玉指，上帝曾多次直接及間接表明她一定會當選，參選新界東是神的指示，並稱3月11日可看到神蹟。不過有關言論遭到另一參選人陳玉娥質疑，陳更斥其「扮信徒講三級嘢」，又指「天主一定會懲罰你（趙）」。<br />\n<br />\n趙佩玉指，2016年在以色列祈禱時，「我親自聽到聲音，主係叫我去參選」，「領導姐妹」亦指天主叫她參選，「係話我喺政治界會得勝，當時有電流觸動我成身嘅感覺」。<br />\n<br />\n反對同志運動的趙佩玉批評平機會，指其支持性解放，故不應採立任何它所提供的數據。她又認為，同性戀是社會的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n陳玉娥在自己主場時間斥責趙佩玉「扮信徒講三級嘢，整污糟天主」，認為她抹黑天主教徒。趙佩玉聞言哽咽欲辯解，但被陳玉娥阻止，「制止佢講嘢，收聲、收聲呀、收聲呀」。<br />\n<br />\n在場的參選人還有范國威、鄧家彪、方國珊及黃成智。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00001/1517804222714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00001%2F1517804222714&d=lcuFvZK4NcesZK%2FZ6r0c4WMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=46a2b3a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00001%2F1517804222714&h=d8119fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00001/1517804222714</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 神既主意"},{"pid":"ba678f176a9736dfba6a0f7364d0883ea3194266","tid":550988,"uid":54264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/185543_60e81bd771d64bf9cbef10aa8c49f81f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F185543_60e81bd771d64bf9cbef10aa8c49f81f.png&h=199bc046&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44bf150cd92a07a56f096080bc4150c607265cf8","tid":550988,"uid":149978,"like"